README - Plus Module Software & Programming Files
Public File Repository
This is a public file location containing all software and programming files for the Plus Module platform.

Purpose
This repository serves as the centralized public access point for Plus Module software resources, including:

Software installation files
Programming files and source code
Firmware updates
Configuration files
Documentation and reference materials
Sample programs and templates

Contents
Files in this location are organized by category and version. Please refer to subfolder names and file naming conventions to locate the specific resources you need.
Access & Usage
These files are publicly available for download and use by authorized personnel, technicians, integrators, and end users working with Plus Module systems.
Download Instructions

Navigate to the appropriate subfolder for your needs
Select the file or version required
Download to your local machine
Verify file integrity before deployment
Follow any version-specific instructions included with the files

Version Control

Always check the date and version number before downloading
The most recent version is typically recommended unless backward compatibility is required
Archived versions remain available for legacy system support

Important Notes

Files are provided as-is for use with Plus Module equipment and systems
Always back up existing software/configurations before applying updates
Review release notes (when available) before installing new versions
Test updates in a non-production environment when possible

Support
For technical questions, troubleshooting, or assistance with these files, please reach out to the Altronic support representative 
